hnic name from <i>flamenco</i> ‘Fleming, Flemish person’ (see   Fleming  )."]}]},{"name":"John","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["As a boy's name this represents a revival of Middle English <i>Jan</i>, a by‐form of   John  , or an adoption of the common European form with this spelling. As a girl's name it is a short form of names such as   Janet   and   Janice ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs. John Fleming was born about 1199, in Monknash, Glamorgan, Wales. She had at least 1 daughter with John Fleming."},"et":{"about 1199–":"umbes 1199–Surnud","1195–Male":"1195–Surnud","1221–Female":"1221–Surnud","1199–Female":"1199–Surnud","Abt 1221":"umbes 1221","1199":"1199","1221":"1221","1195":"1195","about 1199":"umbes 1199","Monknash, Glamorgan, Wales":"Monknash, Glamorgan, Wales","Mounton, Monknash, Glamorganshire, Wales, United Kingdom":"Monknash, Glamorgan, Wales, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1199–":"noin 1199–Kuollut","1195–Male":"1195–Kuollut","1221–Female":"1221–Kuollut","1199–Female":"1199–Kuollut","Abt 1221":"noin 1221","1199":"1199","1221":"1221","1195":"1195","about 1199":"noin 1199","Monknash, Glamorgan, Wales":"Monknash, Glamorgan, Wales","Mounton, Monknash, Glamorganshire, Wales, United Kingdom":"Monknash, Glamorgan, Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1199–":"environ 1199–Décédée","1195–Male":"1195–Décédé","1221–Female":"1221–Décédée","1199–Female":"1199–Décédée","Abt 1221":"environ 1221","1199":"1199","1221":"1221","1195":"1195","about 1199":"environ 1199","Monknash, Glamorgan, Wales":"Monknash, Glamorgan, Galles","Mounton, Monknash, Glamorganshire, Wales, United Kingdom":"Monknash, Glamorgan, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mrs. John Fleming est née environ 1199, à Monknash, Glamorgan, Galles. Elle a eu au moins 1 fille avec John Fleming."},"de":{"about 1199–":"um 1199–Verstorben","1195–Male":"1195–Verstorben","1221–Female":"1221–Verstorben",